      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-4 mb-6">How to Convert a Flask App to Mobile Apps for iOS and Android</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">Have you ever wondered about how to convert a Flask web app to a native mobile app? There's a simple, quick and effective way to get the job done.</p>
    </div>
